    "body": "for IE11 you'd write that code like this: \r\n\r\n```js\r\ntransformData: {\r\n        item: function(item) {\r\n          //console.log(item);\r\n          /* eslint-disable no-param-reassign */\r\n          item.price = priceReplace(item.price);\r\n          item.starsLayout = getStarsHTML(item.rating);\r\n          return item;\r\n        },\r\n      },\r\n```\r\n\r\nP.S.: take a look at [babel](https://babeljs.io) for transforming your code (our library should be working, except the examples, which indeed need to be transformed) for older browsers.\r\n\r\nFeel free to continue commenting for other issues regarding this. ",
